{"tid":761893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"彭梓嘉：落旺角唱歌並非為錢","createTime":"2018-07-30T19:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T23:19:41.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bcaff5bee40ed858b131845ce6661dff374185","tid":761893,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"彭梓嘉不喜歡「賣藝」，伸手問觀眾取賞錢。「當我唱得好有氣氛，好多人圍住的時候，他們就攞住個兜出去問人攞錢，感覺利用我們唱歌的時候賺錢。」她說當時每次見到這場面，心裏總有點難過。「我在此唱歌本意是想以音樂與聽眾打成一片，若講錢，就扭曲了街頭藝術表演的定義。」<br />\n<br />\n#巴打們可以話我知佢手上既既係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/216712/菜街沒落2-最後高歌-不再猶豫-彭梓嘉-我們在旺角情誼深厚\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2F216712%2F%E8%8F%9C%E8%A1%97%E6%B2%92%E8%90%BD2-%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AB%98%E6%AD%8C-%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%8C%B6%E8%B1%AB-%E5%BD%AD%E6%A2%93%E5%98%89-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%83%85%E8%AA%BC%E6%B7%B1%E5%8E%9A&d=8jNF8LvAKg6eO0Lhniy7sWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d20cfa56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/216712/菜街沒落2-最後高歌-不再猶豫-彭梓嘉-我們在旺角情誼深厚</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/030727_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F030727_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=7179937d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/030728_27fce648743beed7f0febd1cd2994fe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F030728_27fce648743beed7f0febd1cd2994fe3.jpg&h=7149abac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/030728_6f9860ab45837cfdc09136ad528df852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.es